body_html: My code runs 10x slower (10 seconds vs 1 second) with trace_level=tf.RunOptions.FULL_TRACE. The code includes rather heavy computation such as large matrix multiplications, and I am very surprised that the overhead of profiling is so huge. Can anybody comment on this?
